I"<p>安装 HAProxy:</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">sudo apt-get install haproxy</code></p>

<p>编辑配置文件 /etc/haproxy/haproxy.cfg</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>global
        ulimit-n  51200

defaults
        log global
        mode    tcp
        option  dontlognull
        contimeout 1000
        clitimeout 150000
        srvtimeout 150000

frontend ss-in
        bind *:8388
        default_backend ss-out

backend ss-out
        server server1 222.222.222.222:2222 maxconn 20480
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>启动服务：</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">service haproxy restart</code></p>

<p>或者</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">haproxy -f /etc/haproxy/haproxy.cfg</code></p>

:ET